 CD32 joypad controls:
 
 - blue/second button: jump (if CUSTOM2=1)
 - play: pause (P)
 - reverse+forward: quit current game (ESC)
 - forward+yellow: skip level (if relevant trainer option is set)
 - forward+green: refresh energy (if relevant trainer option is set)
 - reverse+forward+play: quit to workbench (during game & menu)
 - during menu: reverse: toggle music on/off (F1)
 - during menu: forward: toggle sfx on/off (F2)
 
